==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Alackaday
<hw>A*lack"a*day`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>interj.</pos> <ety>[For
<ets>alack the day</ets>. Cf. Lackaday.]</ety> <def>An exclamation
expressing sorrow.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ Shakespeare has ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>alack</xex> the day⟦rdquo⟧
and ⟦ldquo⟧<xex>alack</xex> the heavy day.⟦rdquo⟧ Compare ⟦ldquo⟧woe
worth the day.⟦rdquo⟧</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Alacrify</ent>⟦br⟧
